<title>WHEN THE BRIDEGROOM COMES</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Doh is G Welsh Tune Book - T.S. 274

[V2]
 1. Aw Pathien! Hinna Thupha chuh nei piei,
 Ka kipak zing tau - Tuhin,
 Hallelujah, Amen.

[V3]
 2. Gamtin, muoltin ah muikhuo thim bang zing,
 Hinna Ni A eng - Isu,
 Hallelujah, Amen.

[V4]
 3. Phungguol, namtin chung hun salhvak hen la,
 Van Hinna Ni eng-Isu'n,
 Hallelujah, Amen.</lyrics>
</song>